race.description: Rmbl Investments Rising Stars Race Handicap
race.comment: PRIVATE JUMBO (1) set to peak at his third run back after racing with distinction in town last campaign. Shouldered the 60kg when up quickly in trip for a plugging seventh over 1500m at Cranbourne a week-and-a-half ago. Gets out to his right distance range now and will hold a forward position with the claim. Genuine top-three prospect. ART 'N' SOUL (4) comes here in peak condition and his lone victory came at this course and distance. Three weeks between runs when back in trip for a battling third over 1600m at Cranbourne. Kept fresh again and gets another chance. QUITE THE LASS (5) kept fresh and since fitted with a jump out after fading in the straight when seventh over 1600m at Cranbourne. Bar plates (front) go on and stays in the mix with the claim. MYSTIC VAMP (7) strong through the line again when a tidy fourth over 1500m at Mornington. Looking for further now and doesn't have to improve much to play a leading role.
